# Hello Notion Git

- **Commit**: `type(scope): description` — type: feat|fix|docs|chore|refactor|test; scope: frontend|backend|widget|infra.
- **Branch**: `feat/xxx`, `fix/xxx`, `docs/xxx`, `chore/xxx`.
- **PR**: Clear title; body with summary, how to test, and any breaking/migration notes.
